Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So this has an impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:01:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So people below 200 are unable to do kinesiology or do it correctly for one primary, one main reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.54,0:01:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about ideomotor impulses and all the rest of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with your brain physiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.42,0:01:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The brain's physiology completely changes at 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to 200, you're run by the animal brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We've done this in previous lectures, and it's in the books, and the current book, and the next book, too, probably, for recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But below 200, then, the animal is experiential.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And when life emerged in this planet, animal life has no means of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.13,0:01:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to obtain energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Chlorophyll came in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Chlorophyll was here for billions of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,out of which arose the oxygen in the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Carbon dioxide, it eats the carbon, gives the oxygen back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The animals came along, and they needed the oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The animals, plants, you're eating carbon out of the CO2.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And the animals come along, and they got some oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.51,0:02:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, the earliest life, the bacteria, have no source of energy inside of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have a backpack.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody packed their mother, the mother didn't pack them any lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're on their own to forage and get, or forage and get.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So the experience of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is always aligned with foraging and getting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always foraging out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking at everybody, watching the TV, checking out the blog sites, reading the headlines,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,watching everybody's expression, looking for sales and bargains.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.51,0:02:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Memorial Day, what is this, Memorial Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.51,0:02:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Labor Day, oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay off the road, folks, stay off the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,More people die, you know, on the Labor Day or Memorial Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Drunken drivers, more drunken drivers die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, in one holiday, than all the people who died in the Iraqi War.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:03:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,One holiday kills more people than all the soldiers in the Iraqi War.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do the alcohol on the highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How to not get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So the aspect then of the ego, the experiencer, has to always forage and sample everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to see, is this edible?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this poisonous?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So protoplasm learns early to recoil from that which is an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,From that which is inimical to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is inimical to life makes your arm go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When she looked at it, I don't know what happened to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The poison particles, she went weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Protoplasm, it's innate to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Animal life knows what will kill it and it stays away up to a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the job of the experiencer is survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to get energy out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to get chemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got to get energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:04:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So the experiencer is out to get and juice all of life to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where it gets its energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego gets its energy out of being right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The little bacteria of the ego now is satisfied and that will feed him for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.95,0:04:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, one nasty blog site will keep you going for years probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at all the fun and controversy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.81,0:04:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to put your picture on there and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's funny, very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, that's the nature of the ego then, is acquisitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Information, emotional feeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the mechanism of the brain then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So the animal brain then is, you see, the input.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the input out there and then it relays to the thalamus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Very fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Very fast to the emotional center.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.61,0:04:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the hippocampus, the memory remembers, boy, that was good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.87,0:05:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Going back to that place, they got the best cheeseburgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the slow part is through the prefrontal cortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.05,0:05:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So when man emerged then, man emerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.52,0:05:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just on the History Channel the other night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where I get my education.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Three and a half million years ago or was it three and a half billion?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Million or billion, don't make any difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Million, billion, one of those numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Arose, what was her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy is the oldest living humanoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So off comes the hominid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, the celebration was getting up on hind legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This left two that you don't need for walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So now these two can feed the ego, the experiencer as probes and information gatherer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And then with the emergence of the thumb, you're able to handle tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've got curiosity, learning, and tool capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The emergence of the thumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So life then emerges.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you calibrate the level of consciousness of all of life as we did throughout the archeologic ages,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.36,0:06:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then you see that life got up to about level 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And by the time of the birth of the Buddha, it was up to about 100 at the time of birth of Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly rose over the centuries to 190 where it stayed until the late 80s.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly jumped to 205, now 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.90,0:06:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So now 207.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.90,0:06:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is the way the brain handles things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And you notice it's slow through the cerebral cortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So when the cortex was added, it was added onto the old animal brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.05,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So now, below 200, intelligence is used to serve the animal instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How to kill you better, how to get even, how to make more money, how to raid your bank account,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,how to make, they call you for your bank number because you just won money or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and then raid it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.18,0:07:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So that, the thing is this cortex came in like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They came in late in the game and they didn't remove the animal and replace it with the cortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They put it on the front of the animal and now you've got a really dangerous animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,An animal that can really think, man, you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.27,0:07:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuclear bombs and God knows what all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, interesting here, you see, is the fast relay is to the emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning was Bush hates blacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason they're having this problem is because Bush hates blacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you appoint Secretary of State, idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is slow because the person reacts with anger, grabs the nearest tools he can to throw at somebody like a monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He just grabs anything, throws the ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this, see, this is slow to the cortex, slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, he gets home and he thinks that wasn't such a smart thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe on TV or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that wasn't the smartest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see the kids pushing these baskets and they're smiling at the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, then the police are going to find out who they are, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:09:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, so quick angry and blow up and so late smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So quick to emotionally react.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.80,0:09:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And then later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Later think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 200 now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.80,0:09:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You see the fast track is to the cerebral cortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's delayed to the emotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So you think first before you react.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the most important thing that happens at 200 is the emergence of the Kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual energy now flows for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, we just learned recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Outside the opening of the third eye of the Buddhic body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.00,0:09:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a very high spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you have to be up 700 or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.00,0:09:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it says the third eye of discernment begins opening at level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't have to wait until you're a Buddha to discern appearance from essence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:10:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So at level 200 now, you're beginning to relinquish the ego gain enough to get a sense of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.09,0:10:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So we call that a sense of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A sense of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The fast track is now to the cerebral cortex.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then to the emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you have the emergence here of the etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.73,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So at 200, the Kundalini energy now shifts your whole brain physiology from left brain to right brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The emergence of this particular energy is the so-called Kundalini energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's accompanied by the emergence of the etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a physical brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,An etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So the etheric brain doesn't emerge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask this in front of this audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The etheric brain emerges at level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not protoplasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Not protoplasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not within the linear Newtonian paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The etheric brain is pure energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.74,0:11:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an energy system.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not protoplasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not physical.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the emergence of the etheric body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, importantly, spiritually, the soul of the etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Very, very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.80,0:11:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, here we see below 200, we see all the different physiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We were saying, you know, aside from kinesiology, you can calibrate things by many other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because here, below 200, you have left brain dominance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your world is linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're subject to stress and address.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're subject to stress and adrenaline.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's fight or flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight or flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Alarm, resistance, exhaustion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:12:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see a depression of the thymus, decrease of killer cells, less immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.66,0:12:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Less immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So what could all the people do down there in Gulfport or wherever that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They all ought to do the thymic thump.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll instantly take you out of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.59,0:12:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole energy system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So it creates thymic stress, which has to do with balancing your acupuncture system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,People who are stressed out are more vulnerable to disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So the prediction of an epidemic is increased by the likelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because these people are stressed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.54,0:12:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're stressed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And they probably all go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.67,0:12:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Disrupts your acupuncture meridians.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And brings in disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.67,0:12:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative kinesiologic response.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:13:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So the differentiation here is one of brain physiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The kinesiologic response then has to do with brain dominance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, this decreases the neurotransmitters, such as serotonin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.76,0:13:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And very major difference from right brain dominance, which is nonlinear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,See, this is aligned with the linear experiential.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.76,0:13:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiencer of the ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is aligned with the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right brain dominance is nonlinear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's aligned with context.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.89,0:13:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you go into a contemplative lifestyle, you're shifting over to this side of your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to have to come to a judgment about everybody I pass on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,An emotional reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,An aversion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,An attraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I witness them as humanity passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I witness them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And I pick up the energy of that stream of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can remain in peaceful equanimity, which releases endorphins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Endorphins then are pleasurable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Positive emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They support the thymus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Increases the killer cells out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the good guys that knock off the bacteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You have greater immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So a person in a high state and a person in a low state can walk through the same contaminated
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,One will get an infection and die, and the other will have diarrhea for two or three
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you really have greater immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Greater immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drink the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pray a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.24,0:14:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Greater immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Healing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Balanced acupuncture system.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.42,0:14:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Positive kinesiologic response.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is pro-life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.44,0:14:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pro-life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pro-life.
