Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pro-life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pro-life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And her arm will go strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The other thing that this blogger did was, you know, accuses me of calibrating these
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice I don't calibrate anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never calibrated anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're blaming the wrong culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If anybody should be hung.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway.
